div.div: "If you wish to return, then you must find all the stones of the Dragon's Heart!" And so, Lee started his adventure to become an unparalleled mage. Which bonds will he find? That's all up to him, to discover...

“Mister Perfect” A living legend in the realm of mixed martial arts, the Champion, Kim Sanghyuk, was somehow reborn in the Murim world as the youngest son of Keum Hojang! “This time, I’ll forge a new legend in the Murim!” Against the backdrop of martial artists and untrained fighters scattered around Murim comes an oddity trained in Boxing, Taekwondo, Muay Thai, Wrestling, Jujitsu, Capoeira, Judo, and a variety of modern martial arts, ready to shake up the Murim!
